R‑01 – Compromised Engineer Account
Risk ID: R‑01

Risk Title: Compromised engineer account leading to production access

Current Risk Rating: High

Treatment Decision: Mitigate

Planned Mitigation Actions:

Enforce MFA on all admin and engineering tools (including any remaining exceptions).

Tighten IAM roles and groups to ensure least privilege for production access.

Implement quarterly access reviews for privileged accounts.

Controls Involved: Access Control Policy, Remote Access Policy, Logging & Monitoring Policy.

